WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.847 --> 00:00:02.046
Arghh!

00:00:04.267 --> 00:00:06.425
You're not real.

00:00:06.560 --> 00:00:08.934
Don't be a putz, David.

00:00:09.065 --> 00:00:10.938
Come here.

00:00:15.904 --> 00:00:17.778
A nurse, huh?

00:00:19.366 --> 00:00:20.825
Shh.

00:00:20.951 --> 00:00:22.612
Come on.

00:00:45.267 --> 00:00:47.343
What are you doing here?

00:00:47.478 --> 00:00:50.479
I wanted to see you.

00:00:50.606 --> 00:00:53.228
- (high-pitched) Hi, David.
- Put that down.

00:00:56.446 --> 00:00:58.983
OK, you've seen me. Now go away.

00:01:00.741 --> 00:01:04.491
I'm sorry I'm upsetting you, David, but
you don't understand what's goin' on.

00:01:04.913 --> 00:01:06.573
I understand all right.

00:01:06.706 --> 00:01:09.577
You're one of the "undead",
and I'm a werewolf.

00:01:10.335 --> 00:01:12.410
Yes. That's right.

00:01:12.545 --> 00:01:14.669
Get outta here, Jack.

00:01:16.634 --> 00:01:19.170
Tomorrow night's the full moon.

00:01:19.302 --> 00:01:21.839
You're gonna change. You'll become...

00:01:21.971 --> 00:01:25.839
I know. I know. A monster.

00:01:27.602 --> 00:01:31.683
You've gotta kill yourself,
David, before it's too late.

00:01:38.030 --> 00:01:39.903
Are you really dead, Jack?

00:01:40.907 --> 00:01:44.857
- What do you think?
- I think I've lost my mind.

00:01:44.995 --> 00:01:50.369
I think you're not real. I think you're just
another part of a bad dream.

00:01:51.335 --> 00:01:52.959
You've gotta believe me, David.

00:01:53.086 --> 00:01:56.253
Believe what? That tomorrow night
beneath the full moon...

00:01:56.381 --> 00:01:58.838
..I'll sprout hair and fangs
and eat people?

00:01:58.968 --> 00:02:03.381
- Bullshit!
- Goddamn it, David, please believe me.

00:02:03.514 --> 00:02:06.087
You'll kill and make others like me.

00:02:06.225 --> 00:02:08.133
I'm not havin' a nice time here.

00:02:11.105 --> 00:02:12.979
You've gotta take your own life.

00:02:14.858 --> 00:02:18.524
I will not accept this. Go away.

00:02:19.655 --> 00:02:20.569
David?

00:02:23.868 --> 00:02:25.742
This is not pretend, David.

00:02:25.870 --> 00:02:28.787
I will not be threatened
by a walking meat loaf!

